item.title: Fri, 19 Jul 2024 11:58:32 UTC
item.description:
Hi folks! Now skype releases a snap file, so I changed the SlackBuild.
In the info file I put a command to determine the release that uses the jq command,
but only to download the file via script. I need it with my automated scripts,
so I did not report it as a dependency.
Hopefully Pat will put jq in Slackware anyway because it is very convenient.
Also, I modified the bash-completion path according to the official documentation.
Enjoy, and please test.
